==>OBSERVATION: Kennel
This room looks like it was once a kennel for a very large dog (some of the bones would fit a dinosaur). It apparently hasn't been used for a long time, as the dust is fairly thick all over. The only exit is northeast.
A gigantic dog collar, large enough for three rhinoceros-sized dogs, is lying amidst the debris.
